//How to Play Build a set Get feedback Win or lose Your goal is to find 
the correct set of balls. 

Drag and drop the balls 
to create a set of four. 

When you are ready 
press 'End Turn' This symbol means one of the balls has: - Right color and right position - Right color but wrong position - Wrong color and wrong position Use information to create a new set You win when all balls 
have correct color and position You lose when there are no turns left
